Psalm 50 has become famous through the wonderful musical setting composed by Gregorio Allegri. 
At the service of Tenebrae in St Kevin's Church Dublin on April 12th 2017 it was sung by The Lassus Scholars as the first psalm of Lauds. 
Watch our video and find out more about the authentic service of Tenebrae, 
central to the Monastic Rite for Holy Week.
